MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Fahkwang ExtraLight'.

Fahkwang ExtraLight Italic (Fahkwang-ExtraLightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight Italic' = NID 1 'Fahkwang ExtraLight' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Fahkwang Light Regular (Fahkwang-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Fahkwang Light'.

Pass

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-LightItalic', Everything looks good.

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Fahkwang Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-Medium', Everything looks good.

Fahkwang Medium Regular (Fahkwang-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Fahkwang Medium'.

Pass

Fahkwang Medium Italic (Fahkwang-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Fahkwang Medium Italic (Fahkwang-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Fahkwang Medium Italic (Fahkwang-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Fahkwang Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-SemiBoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Fahkwang SemiBold Italic (Fahkwang-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Fahkwang' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Fahkwang SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Fahkwang Bold (Fahkwang-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Fahkwang-Bold', Everything looks good.
